"It’s either vote volunteer and uphold democratic institutions or be sucked back into authoritarianism. It is easy to forget that democracy doesn’t just happen—it requires people to care about the institutions otherwise they start to disappear as soon as the first power-hungry unscrupulous populist comes along.
